get.description:
Returns all the links for a specific configuration item {ci_id}

Further use: max_depth parameter limits the number of links to follow when fetching linked configuration items.

NB: for now, only one level (direct links) is returned

Returns the record of "E_Your_table" corresponding to the primary key {id}

The table __must__ have a primary key.


Example: http://your_server/api/v1/account/E_Your_Table/12452
